\c 137
\s Kuchema kwevana vaIsraeri vakatapwa
\p
\v 1 Panzizi dzeBhabhironi, ipapo takagara, hongu takachema misodzi patairangarira Ziyoni.
\v 2 Pamikonachando mukati madzo takaturika mbira dzedu.
\v 3 Nokuti ipapo avo vakatitapa vakakumbira kwatiri mashoko erwiyo, nevakatipamba \add vakakumbira\add* mufaro, \add vachiti\add*: Tiimbireiwo rwiyo rweZiyoni.
\p
\v 4 Tingaimba sei rwiyo rwaJehovha munyika yautorwa?
\v 5 Kana ndikakukanganwa, iwe Jerusarema, ruoko rwangu rwerudyi ngarukanganwe \add umhizha\add*.
\v 6 Rurimi rwangu ngarunamatire kumatadzo angu, kana ndikasakurangarira, kana ndisingasimudziri Jerusarema pamusoro pemufaro wangu mukuru.
\v 7 Rangarirai, Jehovha, vana VaEdhomu pamusoro pezuva reJerusarema; ivo, vakati: Putsai, putsai, kusvika panheyo dzaro.
\v 8 Iwe mukunda weBhabhironi, wava kuzoparadzwa; wakaropafadzwa achatsiva kwauri zviito zvawakaita kwatiri.
\v 9 Wakaropafadzwa achabata ndokurovera vana vako padombo.